Triceradon sat in dinosaur mode grazing in a grassy field. He loved the peace 
and quiet. Everyonce in a while he heard a Maximal call on his comm. 
Apparently they were in a battle. And apparently it was getting worce for 
them. 
Triceradon sighed. Maybe he should go and help them. 
But it was so peacefull and quiet here. 
He quickly shook his head. How could he even think about staying here when 
his fellow Maximals were in trouble? I must help them, he decided. He got up 
and called into his comm, "Don't worry fellow Maximals. I'm coming." he said 
as he headed toward their location.
